INSERT INTO KeyMoment VALUES('cmhyowvj901at3j6gv36ky16g','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr',232,'negative','productKnowledge','Agent showed uncertainty about claims timeframe policy, undermining confidence','I''m not sure what the time frame is for claims so I mean if it''s. You can certainly sort of investigate it potentially if you wanted to do that.',1763114604454);
INSERT INTO KeyMoment VALUES('cmhyowvj901au3j6gsdwoi3k3','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr',520,'positive','rapport','Agent engaged in warm, personalized conversation about anticipation and modern life','I was thinking back to. There''s a film called Victoria which is about Queen Victoria... And it was just like the relationship that she had with her husband and it was all like letters and it''s months go. Months went on end and whatever anticipation I thought. Yeah, that was completely lost these days.',1763114604454);
INSERT INTO KeyMoment VALUES('cmhyowvj901av3j6g2fr228tg','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr',721,'positive','tcfCompliance','Agent encouraged customer to review documents before committing, demonstrating TCF principles','Much rather you''d be happy that everything''s in place than go ahead and not be.',1763114604454);
INSERT INTO KeyMoment VALUES('cmhyowvj901aw3j6grhu05ktb','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr',1543,'positive','needsDiscovery','Agent proactively explored additional coverage needs for unspecified items','So, for example, if you''ve got a laptop at £500 and a mobile phone at £500 and then another mobile phone at £500. So in total it would be £1,500 of total amount of unspecified items with the single highest value of 500 pounds as one of them.',1763114604454);
INSERT INTO KeyMoment VALUES('cmhyowvj901ax3j6gyikr1yte','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr',1769,'negative','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent failed to explain cooling-off rights or cancellation terms proactively during sales process','So what would there be for the refund for that side of it? There wouldn''t be a refund on the top upside, but there would be a pro rata refund of anything you''ve not used on the main part of the policy.',1763114604454);
INSERT INTO KeyMoment VALUES('cmhyowvj901ay3j6gvs06nrgy','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr',1774,'negative','mandatoryDisclosures','Agent only mentioned cancellation charge reactively when customer asked, not as proactive disclosure','And then There''ll be a 30 pound cancellation charge after the first 14 days on the policy as well.',1763114604454);
INSERT INTO KeyMoment VALUES('cmhyowvj901az3j6gv186hjpb','cmhyowvj801al3j6g9y5fcnqr',1769,'positive','objectionHandling','Agent acknowledged customer''s concern about cost disparity between payment methods','It''s terrible, isn''t it? When you haven''t got money you end up paying more. When you''ve got money, you pay less. It''s very unfair. It''s a very unfair system.',1763114604454);
